downloadTitle: SQL Server Migration Assistant for Datazen
downloadDescription: This tool is designed to help organizations migrate their existing Datazen Server content, including dashboards and KPI’s, to a SQL Server 2016 Reporting Services server.
detailsSection: This tool is designed to help organizations migrate their existing Datazen Server content, including dashboards and KPI’s, to a SQL Server 2016 Reporting Services server.
installInstructionSection:
1. To start the download, click Download.
  2. When the File Download dialog box appears, click Save to save the file to your computer.
  3. When you are ready to install the product, double-click the downloaded file, and then follow the instructions on the screen.
